        {
          "id": "b74311b16ae_1",
          "href": null,
          "name": "92d2",
          "text": "So many propaganda efforts — we are all caught up in the smoke and mirrors of intentional confusion.",
          "metadata": {
            "id": "1*jtCadDpeXUT5FMoqjQT2Xg.png",
            "alt": null
          },
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": "INSET_CENTER",
          "markups": [],
          "type": "IMG"
        },
        {
          "id": "b74311b16ae_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "b3ad",
          "text": "What is it like living in a world of billion dollar lies? Where the social worlds we occupy are fragmented and insular, giving rise to echo chambers of fake news and a lack of ability to discern what is real? All the while, global humanity moves toward a future nobody wants and sacred knowledge — like that of all scientific progress in the last 500 years, is in jeopardy with the looming ecological collapse of the biosphere.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
